title: Asian Air Gun Championship: Heena Sidhu shoots gold, India cap off on a high
text: Former world number one Heena Sidhu lived upto the billing as she clinched the gold medal in women's 10m air pistol to cap off India's campaign at the 8th Asian Air Gun Championship on a winning note on Wednesday. Â»
